INSTALLATION & SETUP:
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

LOCAL SETUP:
───────────
1. Clone repository:
   $ git clone https://github.com/yourusername/ss-team-portal.git
   $ cd ss-team-portal

2. Create .env file:
   $ cp .env.example .env
   $ nano .env  # Edit with your values

3. Install dependencies:
   $ pip install streamlit pandas python-dotenv

4. Run application:
   $ streamlit run ss_team_portal_v5.py

5. Access at:
   http://localhost:8501


DOCKER DEPLOYMENT:
──────────────────
1. Create Dockerfile:
   FROM python:3.10-slim
   WORKDIR /app
   COPY requirements.txt .
   RUN pip install -r requirements.txt
   COPY . .
   CMD ["streamlit", "run", "ss_team_portal_v5.py"]

2. Build image:
   $ docker build -t ss-team-portal:v5.0 .

3. Run container:
   $ docker run -p 8501:8501 \
     --env-file .env \
     ss-team-portal:v5.0


