TROUBLESHOOTING:
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

Q: "ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'dotenv'"
A: pip install python-dotenv

Q: "ADMIN_PASS not reading from .env"
A: Ensure load_dotenv() is called at top of script

Q: GPS changes not saving
A: Check .env file has OFFICE_LAT/LON values
   Verify admin has gps_control permission

Q: Can't login to admin panel
A: Check ADMIN_PERMISSIONS dict includes your username
   Verify ADMIN_PASS in .env matches input


